      "description": "Looking for your next big project? This vehicle is a fantastic opportunity for a dedicated hobbyist or mechanic! While it currently needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention to get back on the road, it's the perfect blank canvas for someone who loves a hands-on challenge. Snag this diamond in the rough at a great price and bring it back to its former glory!",
