      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior is in great shape with only minor stone chips and light surface scratches that are barely noticeable. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing some light wear on the driver's seat bolster but otherwise free of tears or stains. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a consistent service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner. You can expect a solid, dependable car that presents very well both inside and out.",
